00:29:53.880 --> 00:29:54.680
No tengo dolor.

00:30:04.200 --> 00:30:05.880
Buddy, lamento molestarte.

00:30:06.200 --> 00:30:07.200
No seas educado.

00:30:07.200 --> 00:30:08.350
Debería ir.

00:30:08.350 --> 00:30:09.400
Adiós.

